<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{عَرَضًا قَرِيبًا}</span> ... مَتَاعًا مِنَ الدُّنْيَا، سَهْلَ المَاخَذِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَفَرًا قَاصِدًا}</span> ... مُتَوَسِّطًا بَيْنَ القَرِيبِ وَالبَعِيدِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الشُّقَّةُ}</span> ... الَمسَافَةُ الَّتِي تُقْطَعُ بِمَشَقَّةٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
