<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَتَرَدَّدُونَ}</span> ... يَتَحَيَّرُونَ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لأَعَدُّوا لَهُ عُدَّةً}</span> ... لَتَأَهَّبُوا بِالزَّادِ وَالرَّاحِلَةِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
